1. Ja sam *obučen* u crno. (I am dressed in black.)
2. Ona je *obučena* za posao. (She is dressed for work.)
3. On je *obučen* u sportsku opremu. (He is dressed in sportswear.)
4. *Obučeni* smo za borbu protiv požara. (We are trained to fight against fires.)
5. Oni su *obučeni* da rade u medicinskom timu. (They are trained to work in a medical team.)
6. Koliko dugo si *obučen* za ovaj posao? (How long have you been trained for this job?)
7. *Obučena* si za tu ulogu u predstavi. (You are dressed for that role in the play.)
8. Ona je *obučena* u tradicionalnu nošnju. (She is dressed in traditional attire.)
9. Bilo bi dobro da budemo *obučeni* za planinarenje pre nego što krenemo. (It would be good for us to be trained for hiking before we start.)
10. *Obučeni* vojnici marširaju ulicama grada. (Trained soldiers march through the streets of the city.)